name: GTA Style | LoRA
description:
It generates GTA Style loading backgrounds.

Notes:

  • It is trained on Dream Shaper so prefer that, though it works fine with many other models too.

  • Weight: 0.6 to 0.8 works great.

Prompt: <lora:GTA_Style:0.7> gtasa2004 cartoon of a man, pablo escobar

Character Triggers (might not work because style was the focus):

C9rlJ0hnson, R0ch3ll, OGL0c, B1gSmoke, C3s9r, Tb0n3, L9tin9, Sc9rfFace, Fr9nkTenpenny
